column5: Hope you guys have a safe and fun Independence Day!!
Hope Y'all have a great day with your families and friends, and catch lots of fishes   If you get away from the BBQ's and Bonfires long enough  Maureen
Have a great and safe  holiday, folks. And remember, no smoking near the fireworks trailer!

Thanks folks.   We kinda missed the Canada Day fireworks at Lakair (or so I'm told).  Kinda stinks to have to come home for one day of work this week - or we'd still be there.  Hey Rick - Hope things are going well for ya.
Thanx guys,just having a few freinds over for a cookout.No fireworks though,makes the dogs go nuts. Joe
I have a dog like that.
CHEERS to all our American   friends!!
Thank you for the well wishes. I am off to a party at daplummas house... I guess I will dig out a few fireworks to make joes life interesting.   Art
And that's how the brothers made their first tv appearance..... on COPS.
Have a great 4th of July Joe and Art. And if you need fireworks, just let Rocket loose!
